#. <section class="sutta" id="sn56.33"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn56.33:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 56"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 56"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.33:0.2"
msgid "4. Sīsapāvanavagga"
msgstr "4. In a Rosewood Forest"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn56.33:0.3"
msgid "33. Daṇḍasutta"
msgstr "33. A Stick"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.33:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, daṇḍo uparivehāsaṃ khitto sakimpi mūlena nipatati, "
"sakimpi aggena nipatati;"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, suppose a stick was tossed up in the air. Sometimes it’d fall "
"on its bottom, sometimes the middle, and sometimes the top."

#. VAR: taṇhāsaṃyojanā sandhāvantā saṃsarantā → taṇhāsaṃyojanabandhā sandhāvatā (mr)
msgctxt "sn56.33:1.2"
msgid ""
"evameva kho, bhikkhave, avijjānīvaraṇā sattā taṇhāsaṃyojanā sandhāvantā "
"saṃsarantā sakimpi asmā lokā paraṃ lokaṃ gacchanti, sakimpi parasmā lokā "
"imaṃ lokaṃ āgacchanti."
msgstr ""
"It’s the same for sentient beings roaming and transmigrating, hindered by "
"ignorance and fettered by craving. Sometimes they go from this world to the "
"other world, and sometimes they come from the other world to this world."

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that?"

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.4"
msgid "Adiṭṭhattā, bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ."
msgstr "It’s because they haven’t seen the four noble truths."

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.5"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "sn56.33:1.6"
msgid ""
"Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya "
"ariyasaccassa."
msgstr "The noble truths of suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli5.440"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn56.33:2.1"
msgid ""
"Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ "
"dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti."
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.33:2.2"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
